                            <comment id="14111454" author="thobbs" created="Tue, 26 Aug 2014 22:18:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like this was introduced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3668&quot; title=&quot;Parallel streaming for sstableloader&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-3668&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-3668&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;StreamPlan.isEmpty()&lt;/tt&gt; should be returning &lt;tt&gt;!coordinator.hasActiveSessions()&lt;/tt&gt; instead of &lt;tt&gt;coordinator.hasActiveSessions()&lt;/tt&gt;.  This is currently only used when moving.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14111467" author="thobbs" created="Tue, 26 Aug 2014 22:25:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;7863-2.1.0.txt fixes &lt;tt&gt;isEmpty()&lt;/tt&gt; and adds some debug logging around range transfers.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
